    "ideation": "The siren is an exercise in extreme, alternating polarity and high-energy alert. Instead of a face, Logos becomes the emergency beacon itself. The eyes represent the rotating twin lamps of the light bar, rapidly cycling between deep red and intense blue. The gaze snaps left and right to simulate the rotation of the reflectors. The mouth acts as the auditory component: a siren's frequency sweep. The animation follows a distinct 'wail' pattern, where the mouth amplitude and frequency build to a screaming peak and then drop back down, all while the colors oscillate at high speed. The final frames simulate the 'yelp'—a faster, more urgent staccato burst.",
